因为 $X, Y$ 是相互独立的, 故
$$
\begin{gathered}
f(x, y)=f_X(x) f_Y(y)=\left\{\begin{array}{c}
\frac{1}{2 \pi} \frac{1}{\sqrt{2 \pi} \sigma} e^{-\frac{(y-\mu)^2}{2 \sigma^2}},-\pi \leq x \leq \pi,-\infty<y<+\infty, \\
0, \quad \text { 其它 }
\end{array}\right. \\
\text { 而 } f(z)=\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty} f(z-y, y) d y=\frac{1}{2 \pi} \int_{z-\pi}^{z+\pi} \frac{1}{\sqrt{2 \pi} \sigma} e^{-\frac{(y-\mu)^2}{2 \sigma^2}} d y=\frac{1}{2 \pi}\left[\Phi\left(\frac{z+\pi-\mu}{\sigma}\right)-\Phi\left(\frac{z-\pi-\mu}{\sigma}\right)\right] .
\end{gathered}
$$
